"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Chuck\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3978:\"<p>SlideDeck Users &#8211; we&#8217;re looking for a <a\ntitle=\"Startup Product Manager\" href=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/careers/dt-labs-product-manager\">Product Manager</a> to help shape the future of SlideDeck and take it to the next level. Who better to ask than the community that has supported us and helped grow SlideDeck to more than 100 million impressions and hundreds of thousands of downloads.</p><p>If you&#8217;re passionate about user experience and determined to leave your mark on the Web, we want to talk to you. And while the title is Product Manager, the idea is Product Owner. This new role will own the success of SlideDeck. From the product roadmap to the product marketing and everything in between. <strong>You&#8217;ll join our elite team of designers and developers hell bent on improving how people communicate on the Web.</strong></p><p>We&#8217;re looking for someone like us, someone crazy enough to think they can change the Web for the better and skilled and dedicated enough to actually make it happen. If you think you&#8217;re the guy or gal that has the vision, energy and expertise to take SlideDeck to its next, please get in touch.</p><p><strong><a\ntitle=\"product manager\" href=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/careers/dt-labs-product-manager\">LEARN MORE AND APPLY</a></strong></p><p><strong>More about our ideal candidate&#8230;</strong></p><table\nborder=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5836\" title=\"Michael Jordan\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/jordan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br\n/> <em>You get the job done time and time again</em></td><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5833\" title=\"Richard Branson\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/branson.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></em><br\n/> <em>You break the rules and set your sights high</em></td></tr><tr><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5834\" title=\"Walt Disney\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/disney.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br\n/> <em>You are creative and dream big</em></td><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5832\" title=\"Borat\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/borat.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br\n/> <em>You&#8217;re not afraid to laugh at your own expense</em></td></tr><tr><td\nstyle=\"text-align: center;\"><img\nclass=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5835\" title=\"Amelia Earhart\" src=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/earhart.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br\n/> <em>Nothing is impossible to you</em></td><td\nstyle=\"align: center;\"></td></tr></tbody></table><p><a\nclass=\"ribbon dark\" style=\"color: #fff; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.dtelepathy.com/careers/dt-labs-product-manager\" target=\"_blank\">Apply Now</a></p> <div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=8L3bAIYEAQA:J6sBoqDmQBE:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=8L3bAIYEAQA:J6sBoqDmQBE:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=8L3bAIYEAQA:J6sBoqDmQBE:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=8L3bAIYEAQA:J6sBoqDmQBE:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?i=8L3bAIYEAQA:J6sBoqDmQBE:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=8L3bAIYEAQA:J6sB