. One is bold enough to ask Brezhnev what these nondescript civilians are doing in the midst of such a magnificent military parade. Brezhnev repies \"Ah, those are our economists. You\'d be amazed at the damage they can do.\"\r\n\r\nIn short, just as markets can fail, governments can screw up as well. Zhou Penghui tells you the finer details.'),(3597,2975,'_wp_attached_file','profile_paulene.png'),(3598,2975,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"200\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"240\";s:14:\"hwstring_small\";s:22:\"height=\'96\' width=\'80\'\";s:4:\"file\";s:19:\"profile_paulene.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:3:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"profile_paulene-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"150\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"150\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(3599,2976,'_wp_attached_file','profile_rovik.png'),(3600,2976,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"200\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"240\";s:14:\"hwstring_small\";s:22:\"height=\'96\' width=\'80\'\";s:4:\"file\";s:17:\"profile_rovik.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:3:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"profile_rovik-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"150\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"150\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(3601,2979,'_wp_attached_file','profile_skoh.png'),(3602,2979,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"200\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"240\";s:14:\"hwstring_small\";s:22:\"height=\'96\' width=\'80\'\";s:4:\"file\";s:16:\"profile_skoh.png\";s:5:\