ity to afford it. Knowledge should not be traded. It should be accessible to everyone who wants to learn. We also believe that education should be based on learning, not studying; sharing, not teaching. Having benefited from our education, we are motivated to give back by sharing our experience and expertise with students who wants to better themselves by learning. Everyone at <span class=\"openlectures\"><b>open</b>lectures</span> contributes based on that principle. Think of it as getting the best tutors you could possibly find, anytime, anywhere and at zero cost.</p>\r\n		</div><!--8col-->	\r\n		<div class=\"eight columns omega alignright\">\r\n			<img src=\"\">\r\n		</div><!--8col-->	\r\n	</div><!--row-->\r\n	<h2>The Production Line</h2>\r\n	<p class=\"subheader\">At least six hours of work goes into a single lecture. Here\'s what happens when we roll up our sleeves and get down to work.</p>\r\n	<div class=\"row\">\r\n		<div class=\"four columns alpha\">\r\n			<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/Forming.png\"></div><!--4col-->	\r\n		<div class=\"four columns\">\r\n			<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/Storming.png\"></div><!--4col-->	\r\n		<div class=\"four columns\">\r\n			<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/Norming.png\"></div><!--4col-->	\r\n		<div class=\"four columns omega\">\r\n			<img src=\"/wp-content/themes/olresponsive/img/Performing.png\"></div><!--4col-->	\r\n		<div class=\"four columns alpha\">\r\n			<h4 class=\"aligncenter\">Forming</h4>\r\n			<p>In the first stage of planning, we gather a team of students with tremendous exposure and experience in the subject matter. We sit down for coffee. Many rounds of coffee. Our lecturers get comfortable saying no to each other.</p>\r\n		</div><!--4col-->	\r\n		<div class=\"four columns\">\r\n			<h4 class=\"aligncenter\">Storming</h4>\r\n			<p>It all starts with an outline. What goes in, what stays out, what\'s unclear. Everyone looks at that outline, then it\'s what\'s good, and what sucks. Fifteen to twenty revisions later, we have a list of lectures.</p>\r\n		</div><!--4col-->	\r\n		<div class=\"four columns\">\r\n			<h4 class=\"aligncenter\">Norming</h4>\r\n			<p>Allocation time. Our lecturers know what they know best, so we lay everything out <i>a la mode</i> buffet. Every lecture belongs to someone. From there, we work out the preparation material. More coffee.</p>\r\n		</div><!--4col-->	\r\n		<div class=\"four columns omega\">\r\n			<h4 class=\"aligncenter\">Performing</h4>\r\n			<p>We go down to headquarters at a top secret location. The on-site support team awaits. There\'s this big, scary camera they use to do the recording. The footage is edited and corrected, then sent for quality checks.</p>\r\n		</div><!--4col-->	\r\n	</div><!--row-->	\r\n</div><!--container-->','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','895-revision-3','','','2012-01-28 22:56:17','2012-01-28 14:56:17','',895,'http://openlectures.sg/uncategorized/895-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0);
